replies.author: gooding300
replies.txt_content:
Caused by: java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: net/minecraft/client/gui/GuiScreenCaused by: java.lang.RuntimeException: Attempted to load class bdw for invalid side SERVER（简单解释就是这个Mod在服务端里调用了仅客户端的接口导致了出错）
Advent of Ascension（虚无世界）这个Mod不适用于服务端
请移除这一Mod

replies.author: cp666
replies.txt_content: 尝试重启或更换mod，去官网重下一个
